  "texts": [
    "The etiquette takes into account the comfort and preferences of both smokers and nonsmokers. 6.",
    "-Speakers are advised not to smoke during their talk to avoid losing favor with the audience.",
    "-Smokers should wait for an invitation or be in designated smoking areas.",
    "-Smoking should be avoided when it may disturb others (during performances, in close proximity to infants, etc.).",
    "(…) -Lighting someone else's cigarette should be done with proximity in mind."
  ]
}